summary: A ECE Preset for those who don't use RaceMenu
descriptionHtml:
A simple character preset I made. [size=4][b]ECE required.[/b][/size]

MODS USED:

Enhanced Character Edit
SG Female Eyebrows
Eyebrows match hair
KS Hairdos
The Eyes of Beauty
RANs Eye Reflector
Better Makeup for SKSE
Facelight
Eihei female textures (UNP) -> With mole and hair

ENB used: Tranquility ENB _ ExtendedFX, by prod80
[size=4]
[b]To install, just put the file in:[/b][/size]

[size=4]Documents\My Games\Skyrim\CME_save[/size]

If the name of the file is already in use, you can change it with another one that is avariable, for example:

_14_commonTriRaces.slot

to

_20_commonTriRaces.slot
